"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.6</span> 標題：投槍、標槍、短槍（javelin）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כִּידוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kidon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:18\">JOS 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:18\">JOS 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:26\">JOS 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:6\">1SA 17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">1SA 17:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:23\">JOB 39:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:21\">JOB 41:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:23\">JER 6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:42\">JER 50:42</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שִׁרְיָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shiryah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ὕσσος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： hussos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0955_javelin.jpg\" alt=\"用於狩獵和戰鬥的標槍或長矛\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">用於狩獵和戰鬥的標槍或長矛 (© Unknown - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>投槍是一種短矛或大箭（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.14.2 箭 (arrow)&lt;REALIA:2.14.2&gt;</a> ），比槍輕一些，適合投擲。持槍的人可以站立著，或騎在馬上，或在戰車上，向敵人投擲。投槍的桿用木頭或蘆葦製成。和長槍一樣，投槍也帶有一個金屬尖頭，固定方式也和固定槍頭相同（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.5.1 槍頭 (spearhead)&lt;REALIA:2.5.1&gt;</a> ）。投槍槍桿的中間位置通常纏著一根繩子，並套在拋擲者的手指上。投槍擲出後，繩子鬆開使投槍旋轉，從而飛行更加穩定、準確，而且飛得更遠。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>「投槍」可以翻譯為「投擲的槍」或「輕巧的槍」。</p>\n<p>羅蘭‧沃克斯（Roland de Vaux）提出，希伯來文<em>kidon</em> 是指一種長劍或彎刀。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 在上列一些經文中採納了這種解釋。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:21\">JOB 41:21</a> （《和》41:29）中譯作“sabre”（「彎刀」），但<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:26\">JOS 8:26</a> 把這種武器翻譯成小很多的“dagger”（「匕首」）。不過，大部分譯本都譯作「投槍」、「槍」或「長矛」。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a> （《和》41:26）中，希伯來文<em>shiryah</em> 是指一種武器，但具體所指不詳。許多譯本將這個詞譯為「投槍、標槍」（“javelin”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、《和》、《和修》），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 作“lance”（「長矛」），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Living Translation\">NLT</abbr> 譯成“pointed shaft”（「尖頭杆」）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:29\">JHN 19:29</a> ，希臘文<em>hussos</em> 是一個異文，有些學者接受這個異文，而不接受證據更加有力的<em>hussōpos</em> （「牛膝草」），但大部分學者拒絕這個異文。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
